            "kicker": "Treatment",
            "title": "Olaplex No.3: Hair Perfector",
            "text": "<p><strong>At-home treatment to repair, protect and strengthen damaged hair.</strong></p><p>Global best-selling at-home treatment that reduces breakage and visibly strengthens hair, improving its look and feel. It will restore your hair's healthy appearance and texture by repairing damage and protecting hair structure.</p><p><strong>No.3 Hair Perfector</strong> works to help repair damage to all hair types, and it can also be applied once a week between chemical services to further lock-in the results of any given salon treatment.</p>",
