          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h4>★★★★★</h4><p><em>\"My hair is badly damaged after bleaching it to platinum blonde. I've used it just once and I already saw a big difference. Transaction was fast and I received the product in just 2 days. Will definitely buy again once available!\"</em></p><p><strong>~Aijie, HairMNL Customer</strong></p>",
