        },
        "0e375c02-dca7-4966-979e-191c84de423d": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h4>★★★★★</h4><p><em>\"My hair got frizzy ever since I bleached my hair. But this really helped it go back to being smooth. Highly recommended!\"</em></p><p><strong>~Donn, HairMNL Customer</strong></p>",
            "text_align": "text-left"
          }
        },
        "ad2c5cd7-f3d1-4481-b772-90d31be13a88": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h4>★★★★★</h4><p><em>\"I use this (& the No. 0) when I get color that requires several rounds of bleaching (e.g., ash gray, purple) -- I leave it on overnight (wearing a showercap as I sleep) & it significantly helps take my bleached strands from 'walis' texture to being more touchable & almost normal texture.\"</em></p><p><strong>~Nik, HairMNL Customer</strong></p>",
            "text_align": "text-left"
          }
        }
      },
